{"type":"message","id":"f034aecb","parentId":"e83ca559","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:10:34.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, let's recap what we've done today. We've set up the identity, user info, moved the data directory, fixed permissions, enabled more tools, committed everything to git. Now we should be good to go. Let's ask the user what's next.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，李工！今天的初始化工作都完成了：\n\n✅ 确定了我的身份：龙虾一号 🦞\n✅ 记录了你的信息：李工，高级光伏支架工程师，常州市\n✅ 把 OpenClaw 数据目录移到了 D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\n✅ 修复了权限安全问题\n✅ 启用了完整工具权限\n✅ 初始化了 git 仓库并提交了所有更改\n✅ 创建了长期记忆文件 MEMORY.md\n\n现在我们可以开始正常使用了！接下来想做什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":365,"output":231,"cacheRead":26680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27276,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772521823039}}
