    \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           4997 zalouser.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":325,"aggregated":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\channels\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          14277 bluebubbles.md                                                       \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          10567 broadcast-groups.md                                                  \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           4417 channel-routing.md                                                   \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          35283 discord.md                                                           \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          16659 feishu.md                                                            \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          10483 googlechat.md                                                        \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           5364 group-messages.md                                                    \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          12783 groups.md                                                            \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          10459 imessage.md                                                          \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           3159 index.md                                                             \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           6105 irc.md                                                               \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           4843 line.md                                                              \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           1700 location.md                                                          \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          12950 matrix.md                                                            \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           4764 mattermost.md                                                        \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          32827 msteams.md                                                           \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           4974 nextcloud-talk.md                                                    \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           5761 nostr.md                                                             \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           3640 pairing.md                                                           \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          12665 signal.md                                                            \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          17386 slack.md                                                             \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           3696 synology-chat.md                                                     \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          28162 telegram.md                                                          \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           7122 tlon.md                                                              \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           7098 troubleshooting.md                                                   \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           9819 twitch.md                                                            \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38          13350 whatsapp.md                                                          \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           8375 zalo.md                                                              \r\n-a----          2026/3/3     13:38           4997 zalouser.md","cw