{"type":"message","id":"09375eeb","parentId":"b199be87","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:36:30.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, the channels docs don't include WeChat. Hmm, so maybe OpenClaw doesn't have native WeChat support yet. But let's focus on the user's original question: exposing the local service to the public internet for a WeChat bot. \n\nFirst, let's recap the options for exposing a local service safely:\n1. **Tailscale Funnel**: As per the docs, this is a safe way to expose to the public with HTTPS and password auth.\n2. **ngrok**: Popular, free/paid options, easy to set up.\n3. **frp**: Self-hosted reverse proxy, more control but more setup.\n4. **Cloudflare Tunnel**: Free, secure, no need to open ports.\n\nAlso, since there's no native WeChat channel, the user might need to use a bridge like wechaty, or a service that connects WeChat to OpenClaw's API. But let's first answer the public IP part.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我们分两部分来解决：**1. 安全暴露本地服务到公网**；**2. 微信机器人接入的可能性**。\n\n---\n\n## 一、安全暴露本地服务到公网（推荐方案）\n直接暴露公网 IP 很危险，推荐用以下加密隧道方案：\n\n### 方案 1：Tailscale Funnel（最安全，OpenClaw 原生支持）\nTailscale 是一个零配置的 VPN，Funnel 可以把你的本地服务安全暴露到公网，带 HTTPS 和密码保护。\n\n**步骤：**\n1. 安装 Tailscale（https://tailscale.com/download）并登录\n2. 修改 OpenClaw 配置（`D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json`）：\n   ```json5\n   {\n     gateway: {\n       bind: \"loopback\",\n       tailscale: { mode: \"funnel\" },\n       auth: { mode: \"password\", password: \"你设置的强密码\" }\n     }\n   }\n   ```\n3. 重启网关：`openclaw gateway restart`\n4. 你会得到一个公网 HTTPS 地址（类似 `https://your-node-name.tailnet.ts.net`）\n\n---\n\n### 方案 2：Cloudflare Tunnel（免费，无需公网 IP）\nCloudflare Tunnel 也是免费安全的选择，不需要 open 端口。\n\n**步骤：**\n1. 注册 Cloudflare 账号，添加一个域名（免费域名也行）\n2. 安装 `cloudflared`（https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-networks/downloads/）\n3. 运行隧道：\n   ```powershell\n   cloudflared tunnel --url http://127.0.0.1:18789\n   ```\n4. 你会得到一个 `*.trycloudflare.com` 的公网地址\n\n---\n\n### 方案 3：ngrok（最简单，免费/付费）\nngrok 是最常用的临时方案，免费版够用，但地址会变。\n\n**步骤：**\n1. 安装 ngrok（https://ngrok.com/download）并注册\n2. 运行：\n   ```powershell\n   ngrok http 18789\n   ```\n3. 复制给出的 `https://*.ngrok.io` 地址\n\n---\n\n## 二、微信机器人接入\n目前 OpenClaw 官方渠道列表里**没有原生微信支持**（看了 docs/channels 目录，有 Telegram/WhatsApp/Slack 等，但没有微信）。\n\n**可能的替代方案：**\n1. **用 Wechaty 做桥接**：用 Wechaty（https://wechaty.js.org/）写一个简单的机器人，把微信消息转发到 OpenClaw 的 API，再把回复发回微信\n2. **用第三方微信机器人平台**：比如 WxBot、itchat 等，连接到 OpenClaw 的 HTTP API\n3. **等官方支持**：以后 OpenClaw 可能会加微信渠道\n\n---\n\n你想先试试哪个暴露公网的方案？我可以帮你细化步骤。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":1216,"output":1114,"cacheRead":50488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772523357846}}
